# Test Direct Lending Graph API endpoints

### Serve frontend
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/
Accept: text/html

###

### Get full graph (vis.js format)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/graph
Accept: application/json

###

### Get node detail - Borrower
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/node/Borrower/MedTech%20Solutions
Accept: application/json

###

### Get node detail - Lender
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/node/Lender/Ares%20Capital
Accept: application/json

###

### Get node detail - Deal
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/node/Deal/PrecisionMfg%20TL-B
Accept: application/json

###

### Get node detail - Sector
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/node/Sector/Healthcare
Accept: application/json

###

### Get stats summary
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/stats
Accept: application/json

###

### Get entities list (borrowers + lenders with stats)
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/entities
Accept: application/json

###

### Get entity-scoped graph - Borrower
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/graph/Borrower/MedTech%20Solutions
Accept: application/json

###

### Get entity-scoped graph - Lender
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/graph/Lender/Ares%20Capital
Accept: application/json

###

### Entity page - Borrower
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/entity/Borrower/MedTech%20Solutions
Accept: text/html

###

### Entity page - Lender
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/entity/Lender/Ares%20Capital
Accept: text/html

###

### 404 - nonexistent node
GET http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/node/Borrower/Nonexistent
Accept: application/json

###
